testcase.name: UniqueIdService #generateUniqueIdWithPrefix should not generate duplicate IDs when called multiple times
UniqueIdService #getNumberOfGeneratedUniqueIds should return the number of generated IDs when called
UniqueIdService #generateUniqueIdWithPrefix should throw when called with empty
UniqueIdService #generateUniqueIdWithPrefix should return a generated ID when called with a prefix
PhotoFrameComponent (D) Should display image with src and description when boun to properties
PhotoFrameComponent (D) Should update aria-label when (@Input likes) is incremented
PhotoFrameComponent (D) Should display number of likes when (@Input likes) is incremented
PhotoFrameComponent #like should trigger (@Output like) twice when called outside debounce time
PhotoFrameComponent #like should trigger (@Output like) once when called multiple times within debounce time
PhotoFrameComponent (D) Should have aria-label with ZERO(0) as default (@Input likes) value
LikeWidgetComponent #ngOnChanges should update (spanAriaLabel) when changes are detected in (@Input likes)
LikeWidgetComponent #ngOnInit should automatically generate an ID when (@Input id) is already provided
LikeWidgetComponent #like should trigger (@Output liked) when called
LikeWidgetComponent #ngOnInit should automatically generate an ID when (@Input id) is NOT provided
